com.sap.spe.pricing.transactiondata

Interface IPricingItem

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IConditionFindingManager, IConditionFindingManagerCommon, IPricingItemCommon, java.io.Serializable

    public interface IPricingItem
extends IConditionFindingManager, IPricingItemCommon
    The pricing item contains accumulated pricing information of all pricing conditions and provides methods which are working on all pricing condition of this pricing item.

    • Method Detail

      • pricing

        void pricing(boolean redetermineAllConditions)
        Perform a search of condition records and then a calculation for the pricing conditions which have been found. Input parameters are the IItem which should be implemented by the (sales order) item, and the flag 'redetermineAllConditions'. If this is 'true' the function 'New Pricing' is performed: all existing conditions are thrown away and a new search and calculation is performed. Usually the parameter 'redetermineAllConditions' should be set to false.

      • pricing

        void pricing(char pricingType)
        Performs a pricing on this IPricingItem.
        Parameters:
        pricingType - specifies how this IPricingItem will be priced (which conditions will be redetermined, which conditions will be kept, ...)
        See Also:
        IPricingType

      • addPricingCondition

        IPricingCondition[] addPricingCondition(java.lang.String condTypeName,
                                        java.math.BigDecimal condRate,

                                        java.lang.String prUnitName,

                                 throws ManualChangeNotAllowedException,
                                        ConversionMissingDataException
        This method combines the three methods addPricingCondition(String) and IPricingCondition.changeConditionRate(BigDecimal, String, BigDecimal, String) and IPricingItem#changeCalculationType(char). This method was created for SAP Note 1294785.
        Parameters:
        condTypeName - The name of the condition type.
        condRate - The Condition Rate.
        unitName - The Condition Currency.
        prUnitValue - The Condition Pricing Unit.
        prUnitName - The Condition Unit.
        calculationType - The calculation type.
        Returns:
        A list of IPricingCondition.
        Throws:
        ManualChangeNotAllowedException
        ConversionMissingDataException
